author: Last, First
title: Title with \{Brace and \"Quote and % ignored comment
note:
An example note with a URL containing underscores,
    which pybtex+latexcodec would incorrectly try to decode:
    \url{https://example.com/some_path_with_underscores}.
    Not that pybtex and latexcodec are to blame.
    LaTeX is just such a mess!
